Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:54.17,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}A morning impurified dully,is starving
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:20:00.84,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}A night to be stained by the merciless dark
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:07.07,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}The orbit this planet goes into is destined
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:13.35,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}To be a distorted circle,forever
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:19.94,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}I curse today I am living on,cause it's same as yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:25.17,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}The uncertainty of tomorrow I fear for
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:29.59,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Moment I realized that it all had been collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:35.26,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}I do nothing but I stand frozen there
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:11.26,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}A yoke to weigh down those who living with burdens
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:17.94,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Equally,ties everyone down to the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.06,0:21:24.27,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}A struggle to call down a curse on his fate
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:30.78,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Like the dead mob rising to its feet on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:34.46,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Break today down I'been living for
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:36.81,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}It'll be the same old yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:42.03,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}The uncertainty of tomorrow got shattered
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:46.58,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Even if you look down and shut your heart to it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:52.28,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}The fangs starving for blood never be gone away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:59.18,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}In this world,it's about to fall into ruin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:02.34,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Dead that's in vain wriggles and crawls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:05.12,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Around everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:07.09,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Gonna keep on fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:10.22,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Don't know what it is for
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:13.83,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Having a fear,trembling and tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:18.35,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}I just keep myself together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.97,0:22:33.62,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Sweet mortal world,it's about to fall into decay
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.03,0:22:39.15,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Swarm of the dead groans and roars around anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.38,0:22:44.75,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Now it's the time to throw your hesitation off
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:47.84,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}Still have a fear,but they are near
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:52.40,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(200,300)}I just run through this town alone
