Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,污秽的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因其自身的罪而灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大家不同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位现在还年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与「污秽」是无缘的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是肩负新世界的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 虽然我比不上大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个被完全玷污的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟大家一起行动以后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想净化之前犯下的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 请引导我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我也看到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混沌的彼岸的新世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.63,0:00:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再顶嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 让我们师生同心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.36,0:00:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说多少遍才明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「杀人病」完全就是扯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是政府查不到尸体袭击人类的原因而找的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是应对恐慌的对策
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大家最喜闻乐见的「日本的顾虑」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说尸体真的在到处晃悠了吗 愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定是新型的传染病 错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 怎么可能无端端就发生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:03:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这么认为也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过一群小白想查明真相？ 少来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须让专家在可以静下来研究的环境下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花长时间去研究
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事 我们根本做不来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说你们自己能做到啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么想活命就别被<丧尸>咬到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比这个更重要的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么做 爸爸已经告诉你们了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是你想说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就奇怪为啥高中生会滥用枪械
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护什么的 只是嘴上说说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这班家伙想用暴力让我们屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明世界变成这样 亚洲有无数人受苦受难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥会冒出个亚洲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家请听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我们去做杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 强迫我们的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将杀人合理化的 那个男人的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你到底在说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩不准插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩… 也不想想我们是怎么熬过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放屁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是由大人决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是剥削阶级的猪和沉迷暴力的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是热爱和平的大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们严正拒绝暴力支配！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,严正拒绝！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高城…你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到爸爸的坏话 一激动就跟他们杠上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白费唇舌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 他们难道什么都没看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是紧闭双眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微能理解…他们的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是找骂啊 死肥仔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我我我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们对不想见到的东西 都想装没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不想自己被否定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以大部分人明知道出了事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在他们不得不承认发生变化了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 不过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时他们的第一反应是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时 就算一开始就知道不会顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不承认变化 就不用承认自己的过错和愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在学校出事后 想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 稍微对你刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我上了一课啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不好意思 我可是很坦率地在承认啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 所以才会这么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才有资格当领队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说毒岛老师的千金 作为剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起千叶佐那子有过之而无不及
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:48.34,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}千叶佐那子 北辰一刀流千叶周作之弟千叶定吉的长女 北辰一刀流免许皆传 剑术了得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亦即是位清纯婀娜的日本少女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使直接触碰 亦不会玷污此刀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实稀罕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弯度轻微
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃纹并未浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锋两刃 小乌造
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小铳兼正…我认为是村田刀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害 好眼力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明治中叶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称为「村田铳」而知名的村田少将
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在东京炮兵工厂所造的其中一把
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说砍猪骨能一刀两断 刀刃丝毫不缺口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一饱眼福了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它已归你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自知无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但无正当理由 我不能收下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:08:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾受毒岛老师指点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此乃谢礼 这个回答你满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这刀应赠予父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是毒岛家的千金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有如实相告了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小女子的肤浅智慧 让您见笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必你已猜到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于我那不成器的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽曾救过她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也多亏了她 才能幸免于难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这么想保护她 让她待在身边不更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高城家千金 由衷敬爱父母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能说我们父女太相似吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就更应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又或者交付给孝…小室 而不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才是我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他自小我便认识
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也知道他长成了一个好青年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你如此信赖他 更说明了这点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得出他现在还有迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在非常时期领导人们的应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算推我当领队…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上就这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽 没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勉强自己 反而会留手尾的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很依赖你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也很勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学校也是 其他时候也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是豁出去罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没什么优点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,论战斗 强手有冴子姐和平野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也算得上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 沙耶够醒目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静香老师怎么说也是个医生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教你一条女人的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是可爱的男人 或者是会宠自己的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他更重要的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我两边都不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定以前是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个我承认
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:10:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算嘴上说些很绝望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了关键时刻 会勇敢地跳出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要任何理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为你知道必须这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂的 阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是我没察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定之前就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概…肯定就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了跟你在一起 我可以做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你喜欢上其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不这样做 我就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道是该高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是该生气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太现实了 这理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人就是这么现实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛吧 还是应该好好躺躺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让老师看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好好想想我那番话的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感受到气息 就在等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没听见声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐也跟他说说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计阿孝会更开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能别叫我学姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本我们就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别提这事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想想起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生还者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从学校逃出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无处可去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊 求求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上解除路障
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都要去找家人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 父亲出远门了 只能祈求他没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:14:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过母亲从骚乱开始推算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该在荷床第三小学上班
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽的… 宫本的父亲是警察
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去东区警署的话 应该会明白事情缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她母亲应该据守在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去搜救以后 你又有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们后天清早就要出发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在留在都市部太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在时限之前找齐人回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人数太多的话 照顾不过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时如果家人需要帮助 我会留下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果到了出发时间我还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就请你当我已经决心留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这身打扮也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:14:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是一直都在算着时机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天然呆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冴…冴子姐 虽然感觉相当不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你准备得也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该帮得上忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 就算要带上家人回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有一定程度的人数 是无法引导的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是没错啦…丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到这时会救到紫藤议员的少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这状况 没工夫去想选举的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我只是一介教师罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带存活的学生逃离学校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 这是教师的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是受令尊的熏陶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:06.86,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(680,1260)\pos(10,85)\an7\fsp2\blur1.5\bord0\shad0\c&H105189}给孩子们一个美好的未来！\N紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.22,0:16:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老头是国会议员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过对我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是个暴君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让妈妈受苦 最后逼到她自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我这个离开家 当上教师的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,床主有个很烦的公安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他女儿似乎在你学校上学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她留级吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做那家伙也会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能救我的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真伟大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫…宫本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事就最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知不知道为什么我长枪术那么强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我也学了枪剑术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,县警大赛中从未输过的爸爸教的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让我爸受苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个无论何事都不会动摇的人哭着向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为自己而害得我留级
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能操纵成绩的 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我忍住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我听说 只要爸爸调查顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能逮捕你和紫藤议员了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你想杀人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还…还想当罪犯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋没资格说我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就杀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟这人的父亲打过些交道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在已经没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你希望的话 就杀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冴子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须由宫本自己决定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了我 只要你还活着就被这事实折磨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我这个教师 能给你最棒的教诲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的判断吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不值得我杀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那些被你教坏了的学生一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长 收到新的紧急行动命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代码666Delta
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代码666Delta
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对目标November Kilo及Romeo Charlie的Doomsday命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:35.89,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}北约标准军事通讯术语 在军用通讯中为了避免听错而使用词语来代替字母
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No.1立刻到发令所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认了吗 No.1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长发令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统命令已经最终确认
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰将实施对November Kilo及Romeo Charlie的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的总统到底是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个接一个变成怪物了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是能源部部长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前天是国土安全部部长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过已经被咬了呢 畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没人知道何时会发生何事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上的天使们 还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝啊 宽恕我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝啊 拯救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fire One！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了 不只是美国
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄罗斯也发射了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄罗斯？ 还有工夫发射导弹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 跟在我们后头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是MIRV
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:43.11,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}MIRV 分导式多弹头 核武器
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.51,0:22:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然数量少 大都市和军事基地会全灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 现在的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活死人之后是先制核打击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在好莱坞的话 这剧本不会被采用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 似乎被采用了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.64,0:23:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 上帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.04,0:23:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界末日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.04,0:23:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(411,430)\fs20}Armageddon
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}电磁脉冲？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}到…到底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}EMP攻击 用不了电子仪器
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}也就是说现在我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}关门
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.27,0:23:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}小耕太！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:31.46,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}这根本就是阿拉莫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.63,0:23:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}平野 女儿…就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.00,0:23:35.92,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天起 夜晚将会成为真正的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.83,0:23:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
